      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a rebranding strategy for a high-end luxury watch line, something in the tier of Patek Philippe. i need to get really specific with our target persona for the global campaign. can you draft a detailed profile of the \"ideal consumer\" for us? i need to know their typical lifestyle, interests, social standing, and also their general ethnic and cultural background to make sure the imagery we use is perfectly aligned with the brand's prestige. thanks.",
